urdu transliteration text:
SHABBIR KO SAJDAY MAIN ZIBAH KISNAY KIYA HAIWHO SLAYED SHABBIR IN SAJDAHEnglish Transliteration
@HujjatELC
Shabbir Ko Sajday Main Zibah Kisnay Kiya Hai - Who has slain Shabbir in Sajdah

