Shabbir Ko Sajday Main Zibah Kisnay Kiya Hai - Who has slain Shabbir in Sajdah

Khaimay Bhi Jaalahay Toh Ridayen Bhi UthariSyedaniya Saar Nangay Khari Roti Thi SaariHindu Thay Yahudi Thay Isayi Ya Koyi AurItna To Bata Do Yeh Gunah Kisnay Kiya Hai
@HujjatELC
Shabbir Ko Sajday Main Zibah Kisnay Kiya Hai - Who has slain Shabbir in Sajdah

Baysheer Kay Halqoom Pe Jab Teer Laga ThaAur Pyaas Se Masoom Ka Haye Khuskh Gala ThaAsghar Nay Zubaan Honton Pay Jab Peri Thi LogoTab Khoon Se Tar Khuskh Gala Kisnay Kiya Hai
@HujjatELC
Shabbir Ko Sajday Main Zibah Kisnay Kiya Hai - Who has slain Shabbir in Sajdah

Apno Kay Bhi Maiyat Pay Nah Tum Ashkh BahaoNa Pursa-ay Shabbir Peh Nah Pehray LagaoBay Goro Kafan Run May Raha Shah Ka LashaDafna Nay Ka Tab Farz-e-ada Kisnay Kiya Hai
@HujjatELC
Shabbir Ko Sajday Main Zibah Kisnay Kiya Hai - Who has slain Shabbir in Sajdah

Abbas-e-wafadaar Ka Parcham Hai NishaniYaad Aayi Isay Dekh Ke Karbal Ki KahaniJo Haath Teh Zahra Ki Duawon Kah NateejaUn Haathon Ko Shaahno Seh Juda Kisnay Kiya Hai
@HujjatELC
Shabbir Ko Sajday Main Zibah Kisnay Kiya Hai - Who has slain Shabbir in Sajdah
